evidence.text: the Court GRANTS in part and DENIES in part Plaintiffs' Motion and enters a STAY enjoining certain provisions of the Rule from taking effect on August 25, 2025.

extracted.value: GRANTS in part and DENIES in part Plaintiffs' Motion for a stay under 5 U.S.C. § 705 or, in the alternative, for a preliminary injunction, and enters a STAY enjoining certain provisions of the Rule from taking effect on August 25, 2025.
